trans-unit.source: Defines an interface that can be implemented in a type in order to preload the type in an ASP.NET application that is running on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Definerer et grensesnitt som kan være implementert i en type for å kunne forhåndslastes typen i en ASP.NET-program som kjører på [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This interface is intended primarily for use by WCF applications that are non-HTTP applications.
trans-unit.target: Dette grensesnittet er hovedsak ment for bruk av WCF-programmer som ikke-HTTP-programmer.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET developers who want to preload ASP.NET Web applications should use the simulated HTTP requests in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] combined with the `Application_Start` method in the Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET-utviklere som ønsker å forhåndslastes ASP.NET webprogrammer skal bruke simulerte HTTP-forespørsler i [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kombineres med den `Application_Start` metoden i filen Global.asax.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The IProcessHostPreloadClient type and its methods apply only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For IProcessHostPreloadClient type og metodene gjelder bare for programmer som kjører på [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] og [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Provides initialization data that is required in order to preload the application.
trans-unit.target: Gir initialisering data som kreves for å kunne forhåndslastes programmet.

trans-unit.source: The value of `parameters` can be `null`, a zero-length array, or a populated array.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for `parameters` kan være `null`, en tom matrise eller et fylt matrise.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient> type and its methods apply only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient>type og metodene gjelder bare for programmer som kjører på [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] og [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)].</xref:System.Web.Hosting.IProcessHostPreloadClient>

trans-unit.source: This parameter can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or an empty array.
trans-unit.target: Denne parameteren kan være <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller en tom matrise.
